Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:11.93,Sign,,0,0,0,,Toki Shouzou's Private Detective Trouble Notes\NHard and Loose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Harder! Like this, like this, like THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am coming! Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,'Right, getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap. I wrecked it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mister Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am all fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Telecom Service, a client phoned your office. Connecting you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how were you expecting a call in my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shush!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Toki's detective agency here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, have no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A 24 hour help time limit still is our motto. From now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, it's no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,From now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama's Elf coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you, I'll meet you there in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily the first job in a long time, can I really afford to leave him hanging?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what was all that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a private detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Never introduce a man in your bed before you know his name and profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never heard yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you had been so playful, I wasn't going to address the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are to be my friend, you should have known better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been together for two weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could stay longer, but duty calls me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my sight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Women and their tantrums...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be a really serious deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As even that call forwarding broad had an agitated tone in her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The client?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You surely are a shrewd one,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We never agreed on a code to recognize each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The venue sufficed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, what is he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That client gave me such a first impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It may seem bizarre, but I'd much appreciate if you took it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely an odd one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to befriend that man to better spy on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are all of this man's places,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it as if you were dating a woman in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you already have that guy's whereabouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not a direct approach?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I need it to look as a coincidence, so I need a pro and a stranger for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's settled, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged, here is your advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I was wondering, why picking me out of all the detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you are the fifth choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,On the spot, the previous detectives didn't quite cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you channel geekiness and enthusiasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Geekiness? Enthusiasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly. Still, you want me to play the goof?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So this guy, Tashiro Seiji, turns out to be a real estate agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.97,Sign,,0,0,0,,Shinshu Soba 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like watching a silent movie, only it's a buck instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, I have his profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that tight-lipped guy be an actual real estate agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes it harder for a stranger like me to make friends with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of a single way in to make a good impression, he's that type of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I have no other choice than refund the 150,000 advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, small fry. This nasty stain is gonna cost me, ya know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole! Quit acting unconcerned!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whassat, whassat, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The bastard spilled beer over me and now act carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is 'dat so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Unfazed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, After a few scattered blows, still landing a one-hook K.O.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't met a man that tough in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cash that out as a payback for the stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to make an exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How many beers did you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Two bottles. And two tipples.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You paid this low end pub way too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That one was a good punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As good as your save.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't stay idle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you now short of one place to hang out at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No worry, I'm used to it, by the next week I'll be someplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, how about we resume the drinking at my fav' joint?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Toki, Toki Shouzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, the client's assignment has been fulfilled, without I even faking friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, during my student days, I was in boxing gym for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I myself was once part\Nof a local gym's boxing team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We had one hell of a good time back then, during the golden age for boxing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuji Takeshi, Gushiken Yoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressure Onishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressure Onishi...\NTruly fine times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, He's the fighter I most look up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said, I recently stopped going to Korakuen Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, paying the entry fee was the promise of a good fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, boxers these days have side occupations, fighting merely as a hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A gospel truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The ring calls whom has nowhere else to go, it's either getting good or bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, if there was a machine to weight the soul resolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be the end all of any pro test!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Housemousie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you about to be drafted to war?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How pitiful that that woman makes you frog jump back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever question if that's how it's supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, are you some sort of psychologist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dufus,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My job's private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And your income?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends, different every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no matter what, I won't be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it! I count on you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, the guy's lights are completely out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurrah! You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, we're celebrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A fine ending of a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, just enjoy life, you'll meet even cuter babes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I prefer this place better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure like stiff drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaudy places aren't my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's just hit the red lights district!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, nothing about women...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... One of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel that way right now, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a cold woman that looked down on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's stick with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A sociopath?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't drop a word extra,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That Tashiro guy reverted back to being impenetrable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As though he was hurt badly once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Toki listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of effort to call a detective but less to expound your case to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lucky one, as I am a detective keeping it true with his motto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as frustrating as your trouble is, my rate is fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no worries on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My situation is special...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh hmm,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let me handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,State your name first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Onishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Onishi Shugoro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressure?\NMister Pressure Onishi??
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was... No.\NI am a huge fan of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reversed techniques, like the rear uppercut!...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,See you at your designated place, looking forward to speaking to you then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressure Onishi, to talk to him was a honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,However big of a fan I am, he's still over a hour late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How... How did you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I forget the boxer's face I so admired?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This, is more than 15 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost shamefully since then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As a punch-drunk bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As a fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It confused me when you told on the phone that you are a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't justify running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair enough, so can we talk business now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, unless you dodge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Kuniko and not losing favors with she,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't swallow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been cheated on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she prefer a young salaryman over me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I understand. A rival in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to investigate about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Assignment accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that, I can't be mixed up in these stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you, play along!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in high demand lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll keep either going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Toki calling, I need Mister Kubo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mister Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, have you been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. About time for the next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Checking the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,By 9:30 pm on the 18th bring him to the Figaro restaurant in Roppongi, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,9:30, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You will notify me about that person, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, socializing with my friend Tashiro will fall upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged for last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you available this Thursday evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, every once in a while, I hang out in trendy places.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead, how about tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the payday, so I can repay for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, working?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, tonight got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, come along as a friend, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm going to that bar because of the job offer, keep a low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are we looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't tell yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a gag order involved after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But please, let me treat you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.21,Sign,,0,0,0,,Gonbei Tavern 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Refill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,First time here, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda. On the way from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you aren't in this district for fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In the summer, isn't this place crowded with youth in the afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Occasionally, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However, rowdy visitors are quick to kill the good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dealing with youth can get tiresome, a matter of age probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a good woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a smooth skin texture, despite her mature age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Madam, the bill please.\N- Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She is fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you seem to not appreciate womanhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,An everlasting aftermath?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bar friends are still bound to have some dating experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have one, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That man sure experienced a break-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, you've seen a lot of these, Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You were betrayed by a woman, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the reason of your mistrust?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing of the kind happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you can't recover from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's on, but I'm fine with what I pieced together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it's not habitual in my trade, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a weekly magazine reporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In due times, I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:04.17,Sign,,0,0,0,,Gonbei Tavern 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, please give us the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I recognize that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, don't thrash the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Mister Onishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki! Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You two better run away now, Mister Sunglasses might regain consciousness anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Our bill...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Made it out in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, how uncanny,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What was his deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That man was the reason for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Infidelity frenzies men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no less surprised than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have an idea of who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,By his punch and stance, certainly not an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a former pro, the name's Onishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Onishi? Pressure Onishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was him, he'd never let me land a punch like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lucky to get off that easy, the bastard was well soused.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This fist connected Pressure Onishi's face, surely a lifetime memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ditto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone can brag being KO'd by Pressure Onishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Toki's detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you fine speaking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, actually, I found something of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A real estate advert.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That bar is for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, although the other company manages it, this place ringed a bell. It indeed is Gonbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But the hostess never told about putting it in the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, it has to do with that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning, Pressure Onishi took a heavy toll on the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I'll be on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get in touch later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, I dread that Pressure Onishi is going to commit a homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.56,0:22:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm his loyal fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, this man's prime years are long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, That's the person of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Futaba Real Estate's Satou.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.49,0:23:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This property... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.73,0:24:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonbei's tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.47,0:24:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it meets your price very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Are you in the city now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be really cheap deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.60,0:24:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.27,0:24:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.89,0:24:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.35,0:24:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.04,0:24:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.20,0:24:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one to be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.27,0:24:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, this is my occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.88,0:24:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're a private detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.83,0:24:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, Mister Onishi hired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.54,0:25:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,With what bidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.90,0:25:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, is Mister Onishi often like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.62,0:25:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He goes on rampages every three days or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.96,0:25:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.41,0:25:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor said he developed a punch-drunk syndrome, from being punched too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.46,0:25:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Punch-drunk syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.39,0:25:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Initially, that was the main issue, but it has been getting worse ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.27,0:25:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He is now raving about I having a paramour.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.62,0:25:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, so, about that young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.79,0:25:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be that he asked you to investigate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.22,0:25:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.45,0:25:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Found anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.04,0:25:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.78,0:25:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you about one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.03,0:25:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this place on sale with such a low tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.90,0:26:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting too tiresome...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.99,0:26:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's between me and that man, all the deal's money will go to him as part of an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.59,0:26:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see any other way, but go someplace far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.64,0:26:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.20,0:26:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.28,0:26:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In just a week the deal will be over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.32,0:26:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get him to see sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.93,0:26:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it out, your hatred is groundless as the woman's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.36,0:26:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.90,0:27:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been fooled by her as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.49,0:27:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Mister Onishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.86,0:27:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You all treat me like a punch-drunk bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.85,0:27:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.23,0:27:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You say so as that punch took you out cold easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.39,0:27:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You better disappear, get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.05,0:27:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, until she flees, those will not be the final words I get from that former Middleweight boxer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.76,0:29:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching Pressure's back ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.91,0:29:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That same guy we encountered at Roppongi?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.25,0:29:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, none other.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.06,0:29:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's mind about women other than his.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.45,0:29:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of them?\NWho can be that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.10,0:29:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Our manager, Mister Kubo, will be an hour late, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.00,0:30:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Shijo Eiko from 'Japan's got talent'? In Roppongi...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.54,0:30:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.79,0:30:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.74,0:31:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.75,0:31:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I could tell how a woman had a part in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.33,0:31:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.74,0:31:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.54,0:31:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what a great success it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.11,0:31:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have spared me the shock, if you told that the third party was TV celeb Eiko Shijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.98,0:31:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's on between those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.96,0:31:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought confidentiality to be part of a detective's policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.80,0:31:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.20,0:31:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the rest of the money, for the grand finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.09,0:32:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,'Been a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.40,0:32:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.50,0:32:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the conclusion I expected, but a deal is a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.93,0:32:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves only Pressure to put a check to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.90,0:32:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A boxer with a shattered dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.86,0:33:03.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,Bewitching woman and her shape ups 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.29,0:33:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A week has passed since Tashiro's last call,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.12,0:33:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll stand by just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.28,0:33:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Housemousie,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.76,0:33:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Full of energy, as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.29,0:33:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, I am spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.13,0:33:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha say, isn't she a fine woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.40,0:33:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.97,0:33:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,'Just an article.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.86,0:33:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.94,0:33:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with you, just don't change job from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.88,0:33:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm completely fine with that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.30,0:33:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.38,0:34:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no matter what, I won't be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.14,0:34:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.32,0:34:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mister Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.98,0:34:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.97,0:34:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.26,0:34:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. I couldn't reach you by phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.51,0:34:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That affair with Shijo Eiko and Tashiro didn't go as planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.69,0:34:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.23,0:34:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,By the making of this TV drama, Shijo Eiko had an important contract signed with a sponsor!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.62,0:34:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.04,0:34:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A one-time extension, stating that she must lose an additional 5 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.51,0:34:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,5 kilos?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.87,0:34:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For actresses on american television, it's a common practice, still...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.54,0:35:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As her manager, for her debuts, I tried to get she to regain her early beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.99,0:35:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, she didn't fall for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.15,0:35:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You were going for a ploy to motivate her?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.25,0:35:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.83,0:35:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence the matchmaking with a lover from then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.25,0:35:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you wanted Tashiro for...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.37,0:35:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seemed like a viable idea in paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.73,0:35:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sex and romance, getting those 5 kilograms to vanish in a puff of smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.55,0:35:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And the result is evident.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.58,0:35:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I meant, it's all there!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.09,0:35:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shijo Eiko's new lover becoming obvious,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.85,0:35:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When the reporters started to spy on them, they run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.23,0:35:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.78,0:35:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.03,0:35:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If the girl stays on the lam, we're screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.64,0:35:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Name your tag, but take this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.88,0:35:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll get back to you if there's anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.53,0:36:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do, I am off to get more help! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.85,0:36:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Hokkaido,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.05,0:36:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens in the future,\NI'm starting a new life with Eiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.48,0:36:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.70,0:36:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It is out of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.79,0:37:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Onishi looks a bit different from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.14,0:37:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He might suffer from another fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.84,0:37:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Th- The hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.83,0:37:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Return my truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.79,0:38:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As obsessed with the woman as he is, he unconsciously does it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.43,0:38:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I still remember of our last meet's right uppercut with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.77,0:38:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Pressure Onishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.51,0:38:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That uppercut you dealt me showed how much of a boxer you still are!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.58,0:38:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what maddens you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.19,0:38:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act as you understand!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.06,0:38:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a chance to fight you made me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.92,0:40:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a lie, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.86,0:40:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...Being happy that we fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.74,0:40:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As bad as it sounds, it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.97,0:40:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, I owe an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.61,0:40:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, You have nothing to excuse yourself for.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.67,0:40:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you about one last thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.41,0:40:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.13,0:40:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still deeply moved by my fighting style?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.60,0:40:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it sends chills down my spine still, that's boxing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.92,0:41:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As for me, I crave to see bouts as thrilling once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.41,0:41:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure many feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.51,0:41:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.13,0:41:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.13,0:41:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Night, fists,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.57,0:41:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, the man's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.73,0:41:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything dispersed along with the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.13,0:41:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My assignment ended there.
